div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\"><img alt=\"Twigs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Twigs.png?2fb15c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Monster_Meats\" title=\"Monster Meats\"><img alt=\"Monster Meats.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Monster_Meats.png?c5a3b6\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fishsticks\" title=\"Fishsticks\"><img alt=\"Fishsticks.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Fishsticks.png?122e26\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shipwrecked\" title=\"Shipwrecked\"><img alt=\"Shipwrecked icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Shipwrecked_icon.png/64px-Shipwrecked_icon.png?3f6ffb\" width=\"64\" height=\"70\"></a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Trivia\">Trivia</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Wanda&#x27;s quote for the fishsticks is a reference to Doctor Who, and how one of The Doctor&#x27;s favorite foods is fishsticks and custard.<br></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Gallery\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Blueprint\" title=\"Blueprint\"><img alt=\"Blueprint.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Blueprint.png/32px-Blueprint.png?80b6b5\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Gallery</span></h2>\n<ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-traditional\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:CD_fishsticks.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Original HD icon from Bonus Materials from CD Don&#x27;t Starve.\"><img alt=\"Original HD icon from Bonus Materials from CD Don&#x27;t Starve.\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/CD_fishsticks.png/120px-CD_fishsticks.png?1bc0d9\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Original HD icon from Bonus Materials from <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/CD_Don%27t_Starve\" title=\"CD Don&#x27;t Starve\">CD Don&#x27;t Starve</a>.</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Fishsticks_128x128.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Icon used as emoji for Official Klei Discord\"><img alt=\"Icon used as emoji for Official Klei Discord\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Fishsticks_128x128.png/120px-Fishsticks_128x128.png?c839eb\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Icon used as emoji for Official Klei Discord</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"tabber tabber--init\"><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"By_Type-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fishsticks#By_Type-0\">By Type</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"By_Crock_Pot_Value-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fishsticks#By_Crock_Pot_Value-0\">By Crock Pot Value</a><section class=\"tabber__section\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></section></div>\n\n\n\n\n</div>",
