  "plainText": "Don't Starve\nTogether\nFishsticks\nFood Info\n37.5\n40\n5\nMeat\nObject Info\n10 Days\nCan be Burned\n40\nCooking Info\nx1 x1 x2\n40 sec\n10\nMiscellaneous\n\"fishsticks\"\n“Sticks to my ribs.”\n–Wilson\n“What you see is what you get. Sticks of fish.”\n–Willow\n“Ha ha, is funny name.”\n–Wolfgang\n“Perfectly molded blocks of fish.”\n–Wendy\n“FISH FLAVORED ENERGY RODS”\n–WX-78\n“Give me some tartar sauce and I'm in heaven.”\n–Wickerbottom\n“Elegant dining in a box.”\n–Woodie\n“These should tide me over.”\n–Maxwell\n“Fascinating! Where has the stick gone to?”\n–Wagstaff\n“Spears öf sea meat.”\n–Wigfrid\n“At least we know how to make fish sticks.”\n–Webber\n“Looks like these fish are gonna be stickin' around.”\n–Walani\n“Crunchy and golden outside, flaky and moist inside!”\n–Warly\n“Woodlegs turned th'fish ta sticks.”\n–Woodlegs\n“'TIS STICK O' FISH”\n–Wilba\n“Glub Glub on a friend”\n–Wormwood\n“You can hardly taste the stick.”\n–Wheeler\n“I've never seen a fish this shape before.”\n–Winona\n“No thank-you.”\n–Wortox\n“Why you do this to fish?!”\n–Wurt\n“Delicious, nutritious and full of fishes.”\n–Walter\n“If only I had something to dip them in.”\n–Wanda\nFishsticks is a Meat Food item cooked in the Crock Pot by combining 1 Fishes and exactly 1 Twig. It takes 40 seconds to cook.\nAdding more than 1 Twig in will result in Wet Goop. Adding Corn may result in Fish Tacos. Using 2 Monster Meat is acceptable since Monster Lasagna recipe excludes Twigs. In the Shipwrecked DLC, adding more than 2.0 units of Fishes may result in Seafood Gumbo instead.\nFishsticks are particularly good for restoring large chunks of Health without using any expensive resources.\nPrerequisites[edit | edit source]\nRequires:\nRequires:\nRecipe[edit | edit source]\nFiller cannot be more Twigs.\nExamples[edit | edit source]\n50% chance to result in Fish Tacos.\n×2\n×2\n×2\nTrivia[edit | edit source]\nWanda's quote for the fishsticks is a reference to Doctor Who, and how one of The Doctor's favorite foods is fishsticks and custard.\nGallery[edit | edit source]\nOriginal HD icon from Bonus Materials from CD Don't Starve.\nIcon used as emoji for Official Klei Discord\nBy TypeBy Crock Pot Value\nView or edit this template\nFood and Edible Items (by Food Type)\nVeggie\nSeeds\nMeat\nGoodies\nGeneric\nHorrible\nRoughage\nElementals\nBurnt\nRaw\nGears\nGold Dust\nBerry\nWood\nNitre\nLunar Shards\nView or edit this template\nFood and Edible Items (by Food Value)\nMeats\nFishes\nVegetables\nFruits\nMonster Food\nEggs\nDairy\nSweetener\nFrozen\nInedibles\nMagic\nFat\nSeed\nJellyfish\nBone\nFilter\nAntihistamine\nDecoration\nBug\nNo Value Food",
